net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base

Interface InvertibleRowMapper<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The bound class
    All Superinterfaces:
    org.springframework.jdbc.core.RowMapper<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnumRowMapper, InvertibleRowMapperBase, JoiningRowMapper

    public interface InvertibleRowMapper<T>
extends org.springframework.jdbc.core.RowMapper<T>
    An extension of the RowMapper interface to include information sufficient to bind a class to a row or a part thereof and also allow for inserting instances
